Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I've awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now I have a favor\Nto ask of my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you buy me\Njust a little bit of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to try out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sustain it for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, well, Glühen Rose,\Nwhat are you doing here by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:22.93,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never Back Down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Surely you're not planning\Nto take us on alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see we're being grossly\Nunderestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... What a sad thought, Shenyun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I were you, I wouldn't\Nunderestimate me too much, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom, Ranunculus!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she was after the talismans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Can you protect your partner\Nwhile you're focusing on that move?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get in Ayato's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then what do you say to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it's an illusion!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Letting the illusion go past\Nis a wise way to endure them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then I'll take this\Nopportunity to target your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's where I got a direct hit on you\Nwith my Gossamer Attack earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know how you should be aware\Nof your opponent's breathing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and smallest gestures during a battle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You expand your senses to your\Nsurroundings, not only your opponent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, under the Amagiri Shinmei Style,\Nwe call this state Vijñāna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vijñāna...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since humans tend to hit a wall\Nwhen their outlook grows narrow,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's important to look at all kinds of things\Nfrom all kinds of angles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you go after my badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My aim was a little off, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to make you regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Semiserrata!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're blowing yourself up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to keep this\Nunder wraps a little longer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:05:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you can resist your own powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now, I'm astonished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The rumors don't\Ndo you justice, Glühen Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were too careless\Njust now, Shenhua.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Shenyun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say\Nwe wrap this up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do need to thank you for making me\Nbreak out in a cold sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Glühen Rose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to fight back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a one-sided attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,since she's unable to move,\Nshouldn't she just target her badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is way too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's trying to win\Nby rendering her unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I can see that Shenyun is holding back\Nsomewhat in her attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she doesn't intend\Nto let her black out so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You love to feel pain, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're in trouble,\Nyou should lean on someone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aside from me, I'm sure there are other\Npeople who'd help you out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, then,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who's going to protect you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we end this now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glühen Rose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to break\Nthe seal completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I just managed to get\Nto the second level, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not like it gave me\Na power-up or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this amount of Prana...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I can store\Nall my leaked Prana internally now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's extended\Nmy limit by that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you think you'll last?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably over an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. In that case,\Ncan I leave the rest to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,\NI've reached my own limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two are one surprise\Nafter another, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... you can see them, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do say to this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style\NHidden Technique...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Banish Evil Spirits...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's an explosive sphere woven\Nfrom all the talismans I had!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Needless to say, this is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only one is genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure you can\Nsee right through them now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato! Don't worry about me!\NJust focus on getting her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind keeping quiet\Nfor a minute, Glühen Rose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True to form to the bitter end,\Nhuh, Shenyun Li?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I like to see, Murakumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you can just get blasted to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say,\Nyou did piss me off a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So at least let me do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shenyun Li has lost consciousness!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Therefore, Ayato Amagiri and\NJulis-Alexia von Riessfeld are your winners!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that was an enjoyable match!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato Amagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would be thrilled to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Your Highness!\NMr. Amagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were totally, totally amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down a bit, Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're as spunky as usual, Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That sets my mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know Flora from before, Claudia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've met her as Julis's\Nmaid-in-waiting several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Enfield is always so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I see.\N- Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations to you both\Non reaching the semifinals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seidoukan Academy has more points\Nthan we'd projected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a representative of the school,\NI'd like to express my joy and gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's nothing\Nyou need to thank us for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to express my heartfelt\Ncongratulations and gratitude to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not just as a representative of the school,\Nbut personally, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, please come\Nto my room tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Come along!\N- H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, then! Away we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of proposition\Nis that, all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In order to restore Ayato's vitality\Nbefore tomorrow's semifinal match,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared to offer him\Nsome hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just drag him away like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato and I are going to discuss\Nour strategy for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, what Ayato needs\Nright now is rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- No way! Strategy meeting!\N- It's not fair, Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}H-Hey, come on... both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This year's Festa has a greater\Npopularity than we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we've already surpassed last year's figures\Nfor both the box office and attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Permitting Arlequint's surrogates\Nto compete was a masterstroke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka's younger brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On to the semifinals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magical ticket that will\Ngrant you any wish you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then were you just wishing\Nfor victory in today's match?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today's victory is something you\Nand I are going to achieve on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:14:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wh-What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only made it this far because of you.\NI'm grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please! Don't say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one\Nwho should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because my wish to save\Nmy father is about to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is something\NI want you to know, Kirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father lost most of his body\Nin an accident at the lab where he worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, his brain was unscathed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so now he's hooked up to the nerve center\Nin the workshop he built at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to feel bad for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he's free to research\Nwhat he wants to,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my father says he's happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What he wants to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Making guns for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For you, Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So in a way, what Camilla Pareto said\Nwas on the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because this power wasn't created\Nfor others, but for me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's precisely why I can't forgive\Nanyone who would reject that notion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, that's pretty cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Camilla says there's something she just\Nhas to tell you before the match, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Saya Sasamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say? It seems\Nthat I misread you slightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misread me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I realized it when I saw your match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When viewed separately,\Nthose Luxes of yours are all defective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when you look at them,\Nincluding yourself, as a single weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must admit\Nthat they're without peer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That actually means they're prone\Nto causing more organic instability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, they're not\Nfor actual combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll make you acknowledge them\Nby taking out your clones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If, by any chance,\Nyou two should win,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take back\Nwhat I said the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ferrovius and I have poured
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all the technology we've developed\Ninto AR-D and RM-C's equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if you do manage to defeat them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say your Luxes\Naren't suited for actual combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to grant you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a one-minute grace period today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! He said it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR-D's trademark declaration!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After making this same declaration\Nin all of their matches,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they've won within\Napproximately one minute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A team that's reached the quarterfinals\Nand is also riding a wave of momentum...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's see if the Sasamiya-Toudou duo\Ncan hold its own here, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Kirin, I'm leaving that one to you.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You show them a thing or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Phoenix Festa Semifinals,\NMatch #1...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Battle start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin Toudou... here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin Toudou, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If your intent is to breach\Nmy defensive barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:19:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then it would make sense for Saya Sasamiya\Nto take me on with her Lux.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can switch now, or else\Nlaunch a two-pronged attack—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not this Senbakiri\Nand I are no match for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please find out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. If you insist,\Nthen go ahead and try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So long as you're human, you can never\Nhope to surpass me in terms of reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, now it's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me say\Nit was futile?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa, whoa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How incredible is that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At last, at last,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR-D has come under attack\Nfor the first time in this tournament!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous... It's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please take back what you said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And let's fight fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't mock us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're planning\Nto keep that up until the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put an end to it with my next strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}C-Can you believe it?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now AR-D's on the attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been 56 seconds since his\Ndeclaration! The minute isn't up yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As far as this matter is concerned,\Nyou've defeated me soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to retract what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, I'd like you to explain\Nto me what kind of technique that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It worked because you're a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You used my data and movements\Nto predict how I'd attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and threw up that\Ndefensive barrier, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The Toudou Style features a technique
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}in which you lead your opponent on\Nby reading the breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}sight lines, distance\Nand muscle movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When two experienced\Nswordsmen meet in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}they try to get various reads\Non each other in a split second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But because you're a machine, you tend\Nto merely react to my movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In other words, your lack\Nof combat experience is fatal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's my Kirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:22:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The fact that you didn't launch\Na single attack during this minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wouldn't it be fair to say\Nthat you're the ones mocking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All I wanted was to fight you\Nwhen you were going all-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}it would be pointless for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}41-type Lux, Twin Particle Cannons,\NWaldenholt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}U-Unbelievable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}A single shot from Sasamiya ends\Nin a clean hit against RM-C!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I'm ready to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.63,0:23:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both Lady Sasamiya\Nand Lady Toudou are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, Ayato,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you're spent from fighting,\Ncome to my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Kaboom!\N- Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is how you greedily usurp\Nwhat little screen time Enfield has...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:40.04,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 17\NThe Tyrant’s Puppet Strings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As Ayato's childhood friend,\NI'm the true heroine!
